    "---\n",
    "## UPGMA vs NJ — Summary table\n",
    "\n",
    "| Property | UPGMA | Neighbour-Joining |\n",
    "|----------|-------|-------------------|\n",
    "| Clock assumption | Yes (ultrametric) | No (unrooted) |\n",
    "| Selection criterion | Minimum distance | Minimum Q-matrix value |\n",
    "| Output | Rooted ultrametric tree | Unrooted additive tree |\n",
    "| Branch length computation | $D[i,j]/2$ from root | Explicit formula (can be negative) |\n",
    "| Statistically consistent? | No (when rates vary) | Yes |\n",
    "| Speed | O(n²) per step × n steps = O(n³) | O(n³) |\n",
    "| Use case | Guide tree for MSA, ultrametric needed | Default for phylogenetics |\n",
    "\n",
